caption: Seen in the evening, very suggestive with its little restaurant below. Really very beautiful
It is a very beautiful and impressive place.
1 of the two real mills remaining in Montmartre above Dalida's favorite restaurant

The mill is one of two windmills remaining from the 1930s that were located on the Montmartre hill. There is a restaurant under the mill, and its name comes from the owner's surname. Since 1939, the mill has had the status of a monument. It's worth seeing this place if you're nearby
Pretty little mill in the heart of Montmartre
